                  <collation>
                    <p>The quires, six in number, seem to have been originally signed with both letters and arithmetical figures (see <locus from="26" to="26">fol. 26</locus>), but <ref target="#handNote2">a more modern hand</ref> has marked them with letters from <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܙ</foreign> to <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܒ</foreign>.</p>
